Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:45.16,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}零落春之瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:52.04,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}初见的那份洁白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:58.05,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}永葆纯粹的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:01:03.77,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}朝霞撩拨发梢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:09.81,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}散出炫目的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:15.20,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}斑斓的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:20.57,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}点染初遇的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:26.33,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}视线交汇之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:30.97,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}抑住怦然的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:41.12,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}初次碰触的手指 心头描摹的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:47.34,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}一切都缓缓流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:55.45,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}随风起舞的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:59.48,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}并非凋零的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:06.60,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}闪烁跨越流转四季
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:11.96,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}渲染着未来的绮丽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:18.05,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}春风拂过之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:22.36,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}于这怀念的舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:29.13,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}交错回忆不再迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:34.49,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}携彼之手描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:40.20,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}“新新”相印的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:59.44,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}放学路洒落的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:06.32,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}宛如夜中浮动的月光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:12.33,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}你相伴我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:18.05,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}视线交合之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:22.70,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}默数渐快的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:29.14,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}初次抚摸的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:32.55,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}心头泛起的波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:39.32,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}一切都时过境迁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:09.26,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}回环的时间 遥遥千夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:15.39,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}流向未来的“永远”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:20.88,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}冬窗揽阔的风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:27.31,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}乘着纯洁的梦想飞向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:35.08,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}于春风中纷飞的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:39.40,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}并非转瞬而逝的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:46.24,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}那是来自昨日的赠礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:51.78,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}轻轻推动前行之人的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:58.39,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}春风再次拂过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:02.29,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}于这崭新的舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:09.49,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}十指相扣的二人不再分离
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:20.63,CN-BottomLeft,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}共同续写永不完结的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:40.86,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}開いたアルバムから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:45.16,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}こぼれた春の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:52.04,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}出会った日のその白さ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:58.05,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}色褪せないまま変わらずに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:01:03.77,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}朝日が髪を撫でて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:09.81,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}まぶしい光を散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:15.20,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}出会った日の思い出を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:20.57,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}色鮮やかに描くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:26.33,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}視線がすれ違うたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:30.97,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}高鳴る鼓動を抑えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:41.12,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}初めて触れた指でなぞった名前、心まで染め上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:47.34,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}すべてを変えてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:55.45,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}春空舞う花びらは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:59.48,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}過ぎ去った奇跡じゃなく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.48,0:02:06.60,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}巡った季節を超えても輝いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:11.96,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}二人の未来を彩るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:18.05,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}春風吹くこの場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:22.36,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}懐かしい舞台の上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:29.13,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}重ねた思いの数だけ迷わずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:34.49,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}二人で描いてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:40.20,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}新しい物語を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:59.44,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}放課後待ち合わせて、帰った夕日の色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:06.32,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}夜空浮かぶ月のように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:12.33,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}君が傍にいてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:18.05,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}視線がぶつかるたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:22.70,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}近づく鼓動を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:29.14,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}初めて触れた頬の震えが今も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:32.55,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}心まで染め上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:39.32,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}すべてを変えてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:09.26,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}繰り返す時を、幾千の夜を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:15.39,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}永遠に過ごすこの先もずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:20.88,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}冬の窓に払う風は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:27.31,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}穢れのない思いの乗せて飛んで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:35.08,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}春空舞う思い出は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:39.40,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}過ぎ去った奇跡じゃなく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:46.24,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}明日へ踏み出す背中をそっと押す
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:51.78,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}昨日から届く贈り物だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:58.39,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}春風吹くこの場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:02.29,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}新しい舞台の上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:09.49,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}重ねた手と手をもう二度と離さずに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:20.63,JP-TopRight,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5\blur5}二人で今歩き出そう、終わらない物語を
